{"id":165083,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/泰国大选期间禁止facebook和twitter/","date":"2011-07-03T09:00:02Z","modified":"2011-07-03T09:00:02Z","title":"泰国大选期间禁止Facebook和Twitter","content":"<p>在7月3日泰国大选期间，任何人不得在社交网站上对候选人或党派发表任何评论。如果被发现社交媒体被用于竞选和选举用途，违反者将面临最高6个月徒刑和1万泰铢罚款。禁令还包括了短消息和转发邮件，此外选举期间还被禁止销售酒精。警方发言人Prawut Thavornsiri称，由一百多位警方组成的小组将监视Facebook和Twitter等社交网站，如果能即时跟踪到消息来源，他们将立即屏蔽网站并实行逮捕；如果网站是在国外注册，他们将先屏蔽然后要求ISP展开进一步调查。一位办公室职员认为，禁止表达观点不公平。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/165f62f8/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%B3%B0%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%89%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2Facebook%E5%92%8CTwitter&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F07%2F03%2F060213%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%B3%B0%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%89%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2Facebook%E5%92%8CTwitter&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F07%2F03%2F060213%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/106216512251/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/165f62f8/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/106216512251/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/165f62f8/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=Le-hD1KTIqo:Wsr5Hs6L7Xg:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=Le-hD1KTIqo:Wsr5Hs6L7Xg:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><sm